  <brief_title>The Effect of Gabapentin, Ketamine and Dexamethasone on Pain and Opioid Requirements After Hip Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Gabapentin, Low Dose Ketamine, Paracetamol, NSAID and Dexamethasone on Pain and Opioid Requirements in Patients Scheduled for Primary Total Hip Replacement</official_title>
  <sponsors>
